        Gritty is not alone in mascot stardom - he is the latest in a long line of weird sports mascots that have made headlines around the world.But whether Gritty's 15 minutes of fame will be up soon or not, his presence will be lasting for some.A number of fans are known to have already had the orange beast inked permanently on their skin. 
    
        
